    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>恐怖体验 :</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《V光》是一款2D游戏，致力于为玩家提供在线同玩的恐怖体验。在《V光》中，你可以扮演一个被诅咒的鬼魂，你被困在房子里，使用你的能力去猎杀其他玩家。或者你可以扮演一个人类，和别人组队，找到逃离这栋被诅咒的房子所需的关键道具。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/2f56d02934678327e5e6e3b7909c4de0.poster.avif?t=1763474599\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/2f56d02934678327e5e6e3b7909c4de0.webm?t=1763474599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/2f56d02934678327e5e6e3b7909c4de0.mp4?t=1763474599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>想猎杀人类吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你扮演被诅咒的鬼魂时，你会对光极其敏感。然而，你可以穿墙，藏身在房子里的物品中。饿了？就走向人类，冲向他们，把他们撕成碎片！记住，你的眼睛对光非常敏感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/e4f89b715ab103f77bf6e71ecfa0dc08.poster.avif?t=1763474599\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/e4f89b715ab103f77bf6e71ecfa0dc08.webm?t=1763474599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/e4f89b715ab103f77bf6e71ecfa0dc08.mp4?t=1763474599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>保持安静！ </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谨记，你手中的手电筒就是你唯一的武器。手电筒可以保护你不受被诅咒的鬼魂的侵扰。只需把光对着鬼魂，不要回头！不过你需要谨慎地使用手电筒， 因为电池会没电。电池没电了？找到遍布房子各处的电池盒子里的电池吧。当你的手电筒没电的时候，你可以把房间里的灯打开来照亮周围的环境。记得行动要迅速，鬼魂可能就在你身后… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/a9c523282e8e51fd5336d8bcd2afbf54.poster.avif?t=1763474599\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/a9c523282e8e51fd5336d8bcd2afbf54.webm?t=1763474599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094900/extras/a9c523282e8e51fd5336d8bcd2afbf54.mp4?t=1763474599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色 :</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>•经典游戏模式 </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类试图逃出房子，一只鬼魂在猎杀他们！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>•手电筒 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用手电筒照鬼魂可以让它减速，还会限制它的视野。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• 利爪 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过向前猛冲，鬼魂可以穿墙，藏在物品里，杀掉人类玩家。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• 灯光开关  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房间里灯的开关控制房间内的灯，打开灯可以照亮房间，当开关被关上的时候，你最好加快脚步！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• \t立体语音聊天  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他玩家的声音大小取决于他们的位置，更贴近现实的通话方式，更激动人心的计划… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• 逃出房子  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类需要找到房子中的道具，按照一定的顺序把它们放到大门口。人类可以使用这些道具开门，逃出房子。</p>",
